								<div class="title" id="post-title-4487750">
																		Episode 1
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pastarasta1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2551139); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2551139&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610164521" alt="pastarasta1" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2551139)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pastarasta1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2551139); return false;" >pastarasta1</a></span> <span class="odate time_1580699588 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">03 Feb 2020 03:13</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4487750">
									

<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Image&nbsp;Attribution</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Most images are created, drawn, and edited by me. the &quot;got u&quot; image was took from <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Youth_Square_Y_Loft_Room_2_2017.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Youth_Square_Y_Loft_Room_2_2017.jpg</a> and the last image was created using a screenshot of Creepypasta Wiki that I took. All other images are drawn and taken by me.</p>
<p>(Please don't attempt to write a &quot;micheal the killer&quot; story and upload it to the creepypasta wiki as a joke, mods don't like that kind of thing and it will waste their time.)</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2><span><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FeMFSOkNoSQ&amp;l">You shouldn't have done that.</a></span></h2>
<p>- <a href="https://creepypasta.fandom.com/wiki/BEN_Drowned">BEN Drowned</a></p>
</div>
<hr />
<p>I started this near Halloween, and now I am finally finished with it! This is my second attempt at writing something for this site, and I hope you enjoy this! Sorry if the ending is a bit too anti-climatic.</p>
<p>It's probably obvious what's going on in this story but feel free to ask questions if you're confused anyway!</p>
<p>Thanks to everyone who helped me with this in the draft stage, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2858989); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2858989&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607661466" alt="Westrin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2858989)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2858989); return false;">Westrin</a></span> for helping me out with the finishing touches and letting me use their author post template, and thanks so much to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/natvoltaic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2800867); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607661466" alt="NatVoltaic" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2800867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/natvoltaic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2800867); return false;">NatVoltaic</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3938622); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3938622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607661466" alt="The Great Hippo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3938622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3938622); return false;">The Great Hippo</a></span> for creating and developing Parawatch! (Hippo also provided some crit of this during writing which was a very fun and enjoyable experience!!) If I forgot to mention anyone, I'm really sorry, it has been really long since I first started work on this.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Trivia&nbsp;+&nbsp;Spoilers</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>- Any pictures of micheal, or taken by micheal, will always end up having shitty quality, and end up looking fake as hell.</p>
<p>- michael is very much a huge fan of Creepypasta and loves to read them daily. In a meta sense, he can even travel into these stories.</p>
<p>- If you are nice to michael's and his stories, he won't kill you, and if you're nice enough he might even consider you a &quot;friend&quot;. Nobody knows what happens to the people who micheal considers friends, but they end up appearing later in future stories&#8230;</p>
<p>- micheal is very vulnerable to SCP-2747, he would be neutralized if it somehow got a hold of him.</p>
<p>- michael wasn't written to be a sympathetic character, but it's fine if you feel sympathy for him.</p>
<p>- He wants to make friends w/ other metafictional characters but most don't really like him, cause he's kind of obnoxious and rude.</p>
<p>- There is no canonical way to spell his name, micheal himself butchers it a lot</p>
<p>- His favorite song is <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6PHpCywCcIA">Insanity,</a> and yes, it's about as good as it sounds.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Translator's&nbsp;Notes</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>This is for anyone who wants to translate this story for some reason.</p>
<p>This story will probably be really difficult to translate, so I might make fully comprehensible versions of micheal's speeches for reference some time. Let me know if you need them and I will make them!</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

